Change the ConnectionString setting under 'Application/Properties/Settings'
Compile the program
Copy the executable and Cassis libraries to the VDH server you want to drain
Run as administrator

The server will drain, reboot and then be back available. 
A small issue is that users cannot reconnect to existing VDI sessions if they are disconnected.

As usual this code is provided without warranty, so test/use at your own risk!
